# McLean replication — reproducible from `pipelines/notebooks/mclean/`
# Bronze (CVM zips ~165MB) and silver (intermediate parquets) are regenerable.
# The published gold artifact lives in `app/public/data/mclean_results.json`.
data/mclean/bronze/
data/mclean/silver/
data/mclean/gold/

